{"about_the_game":"Narcotics Ninja is a fast paced action platformer with an emphasis on physics based platforming and high intensity combat. Traverse a variety of levels set in a cyberpunk style environment in which the player takes on the role of a drug runner, who must navigate their way through rival territories and deal with law enforcement.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937970/extras/gameplay_platforming.gif?t=1651484297\" /><br><br>Once you take on the role of the Runner, you will gain access to his toolkit - A minigun, a tool for both dispatching enemies from a distance and navigating your way through the levels; A katana, an effective weapon at close range for instantly destroying most types of enemies; and the shurikens, a throwable weapon for taking enemies out at range.<br><br>On top of all of this, the player will be able to use the <strong><i>Overdrive</i></strong> ability when enough enemies have been destroyed, which slows the passage of time and grants explosive ammunition to the minigun for a short while.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937970/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1651484297","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937970/page.bg.jpg?t=1651484297","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937970/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1651484297","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937970/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1651484297","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Drug References\r\nCartoon Violence\r\nAdult Language"},"detailed_description":"Narcotics Ninja is a fast paced action platformer with an emphasis on physics based platforming and high intensity combat. Traverse a variety of levels set in a cyberpunk